    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.61) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.19)) / 0.77)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.26)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.74) + 0.95) - wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.63)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(tmp) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.52) * 0.85))
    tmp = (wp.exp(v2) / wp.abs(tmp))
    v1 = wp.sin(v2)
    v0 = (v2 / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.79) - (tmp + 0.77 / tmp + 0.58)))
    data[tid] = v0
